title: Atlanta Pride Recap/Reviewing My Old Music
description:
Tune in to hear about Camo’s weekly endeavors before recapping their Atlanta pride experience. Keep listening for more music story times of Camo’s past! 
To match with a licensed therapist today, go to https://Talkspace.com and use code UNFAZED to get $100 off of your first month!
See for yourself why Chime is so loved at https://chime.com/unfazed!
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
